Package net.dean.jraw.http

Contains all the classes which directly build off of OkHttp

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HttpClient<U extends RestResponse>
    This interface provides a way to mark classes that can make HTTP requests
    NetworkAccessible<T extends RestResponse,U extends HttpClient<T>>
    This interface shows that the implementing class has access to a class that can send HTTP requests
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicAuthenticator
    This class is responsible for doing basic HTTP authentication.
    Credentials
    This class is responsible for handling any kind of Reddit user and OAuth2 credentials
    RedditResponse
    This class provides automatic parsing of ApiExceptions, as well as quick RedditObject and Listing creation.
    RestClient<T extends RestResponse>
    This class provides a high-level API to send REST-oriented HTTP requests with.
    RestRequest
    This class is responsible for representing a RESTful HTTP request
    RestRequest.Builder
    This class is responsible for creating new RestRequests
    RestResponse
    This class is used to show the result of a request to a RESTful web service, such as Reddit's JSON API.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuthenticationMethod  
    MediaTypes
    A list of common MediaType objects used throughout the project
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NetworkException
    This Exception is thrown when an HTTP response is not successful
